=\"\" os=\"\" siemreap\";\"=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\">ដាំដុះ</span><span id=\"E577\" class=\"qowt-font9-KhmerOSSiemreap\" khmer=\"\" os=\"\" siemreap\";\"=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\">បាន</span>,</li><li id=\"E578\" class=\"qowt-stl-ListParagraph\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\"><span id=\"E581\" class=\"qowt-font9-KhmerOSSiemreap\" khmer=\"\" os=\"\" siemreap\";\"=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\">អាចដាំ និងពង្រីកពូជរុក្ខជាតិបាន</span>,</li><li id=\"E582\" class=\"qowt-stl-ListParagraph\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\"><span id=\"E585\" class=\"qowt-font9-KhmerOSSiemreap\" khmer=\"\" os=\"\" siemreap\";\"=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\">ចេះប្</span><span id=\"E586\" class=\"qowt-font9-KhmerOSSiemreap\" khmer=\"\" os=\"\" siemreap\";\"=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\">រើបច្ចេកវិទ្យាទំនើប ក្នុងការដាំដុះ</span><span id=\"E587\" class=\"qowt-font9-KhmerOSSiemreap\" khmer=\"\" os=\"\" siemreap\";\"=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\">លើវិស័យកសិកម្ម</span>,</li><li id=\"E588\" class=\"qowt-stl-ListParagraph\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\"><span id=\"E591\" class=\"qowt-font9-KhmerOSSiemreap\" khmer=\"\" os=\"\" siemreap\";\"=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\">អាចគ្រប់គ្រងដី និងទឹកដើម្បីដាំដុះដំណាំ</span>,</li><li id=\"E592\" class=\"qowt-stl-ListParagraph\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\"><span id=\"E595\" class=\"qowt-font9-KhmerOSSiemreap\" khmer=\"\" os=\"\" siemreap\";\"=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\">ចេះ</span><span id=\"E596\" class=\"qowt-font9-KhmerOSSiemreap\" khmer=\"\" os=\"\" siemreap\";\"=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\">ថែទាំ និង</span><span id=\"E597\" class=\"qowt-font9-KhmerOSSiemreap\" khmer=\"\" os=\"\" siemreap\";\"=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\">ការពារដំណាំ</span>,</li><li id=\"E598\" class=\"qowt-stl-ListParagraph\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\"><span id=\"E600\" class=\"qowt-font9-KhmerOSSiemreap\" khmer=\"\" os=\"\" siemreap\";\"=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\">ចេះប្រើប្រាស់ និងថែទាំឧបករណ៍ និងសម្ភារៈរោងបណ្តុះ</span>,</li><li id=\"E601\" class=\"qowt-stl-ListParagraph\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\"><span id=\"E604\" class=\"qowt-font9-KhmerOSSiemreap\" khmer=\"\" os=\"\" siemreap\";\"=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\">ចេះគ្រប់គ្រងកសិ</span><span id=\"E605\" class=\"qowt-font9-KhmerOSSiemreap\" khmer=\"\" os=\"\" siemreap\";\"=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\">ផល និងទីផ្សារ</span>,</li><li id=\"E606\" class=\"qowt-stl-ListParagraph\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\"><span id=\"E609\" class=\"qowt-font9-KhmerOSSiemreap\" khmer=\"\" os=\"\" siemreap\";\"=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\">អាចផ្សព្វផ្សាយអំពីកសិកម្ម</span>,</li></ul><p id=\"E610\" class=\"qowt-li-9_0 qowt-list qowt-stl-ListParagraph\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.5em; word-break: break-word;\"><span khmer=\"\" os=\"\" siemreap\";\"=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word; font-weight: bolder;\">អង្គភាព ឬមូលដ្ឋានដែលអ្នកសិក្សាចប់មុខជំនាញនេះអាចទៅបម្រើការងារ៖</span></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; margin-left: 0px; word-break: break-word; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li id=\"E612\" class=\"qowt-li-2_0 qowt-list qowt-stl-ListParagraph\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\"><span id=\"E613\" class=\"qowt-font9-KhmerOSSiemreap\" khmer=\"\" os=\"\" siemreap\";\"=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; word-break: break-word;\">ជាអ្នកបច្ចេកទេសកសិកម្មនៅតាមក្រសួង ក្រុមហ៊ុន អង្គការក្រៅរដ្ឋាភិបាលន